public class QuizPanel
extends javax.swing.JPanel
Author:
calebcramer This is the panel that runs the quiz tab It has a problem in the middle of the panel and a timer on the top There are also a few buttons and a label on the bottom It is a timed quiz that will save all of the answers they give and return their score
